Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the use of agricultural robots in orchard management.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as some of the robotic systems mentioned in the paper may use computer vision for tasks such as fruit detection and localization.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also possible categories as some of the robotic systems may use machine learning and AI techniques for tasks such as decision-making and control.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of robotic systems for orchard management, which involves control and coordination of multiple robots.
